{"tid":1249839,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【Square Enix股東大會要點摘要】:前年度的手遊和頁遊情況非常不妙","createTime":"2019-06-21T23:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T12:19:18.000Z","uid":75050,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5d6b488b8e7b76ceb196e53031caf2a014085dfb","tid":1249839,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T23:43:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Nmia.Gaming/posts/1269800166521192\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNmia.Gaming%2Fposts%2F1269800166521192&d=ow9JOMNIA3MeF92spim0Pum6EOSy25kVi46SvbSXLY8%3D&h=bf600145\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Nmia.Gaming/posts/1269800166521192</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NurT2BN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNurT2BN.jpg&h=d824c1a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今天早上Square Enix在東京進行了本財年的股東大會，在現場社長松田洋祐以及各個負責人對今後的發展進行了介紹。以下要點摘要：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>● 前年度的手遊和頁遊情況非常不妙，本以為能夠加強原有作品的影響力但卻適得其反。</ins></strong>之後對開發體制進行調整，其中《浪漫沙加 RE; Universe》的反響非常好，不但獲得了非常多忠實的玩家，開發組內部也非常團結士氣昂揚；<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sC5p9g0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsC5p9g0.jpg&h=9876da26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n● 谷歌和微軟的雲服務這些新平台增加之後對於軟件商來說是很有好處的，盡管不會在這個年度就出成績，但今後的預想是很樂觀的。在這今後會采取強化數字版銷售、對應多平台、覆蓋更多的地區等戰略；<br />\n<br />\n● 2021財年的預估銷售額為3000到4000億日元，雖然目前不能公布，但只要知道今後的作品的話都是能明白這個陣容是很有說服力的；<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>● 前SE員工田畑端主管的工作室Luminous Productions是為了開發3A大作而設立的新工作室，但經過對工作室發展方向的評估之後決定變更組織架構。雖然發生了一些虧損，但在不遠的將來會帶來更多的作品；</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v6FQ4Qx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv6FQ4Qx.jpg&h=fd65937f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n● 此前亞洲地區的作品都是委托萬代南夢宮與索尼互動娛樂發行，從這個財年開始亞洲地區的遊戲將由SE自己發行。或許今後能夠提高中文本地化作品的推出效率；<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>● 《最終幻想 7 重制版》目前還沒有PS4同捆機的預定，這還得看SIE那邊的調整；</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEqmr3W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEqmr3W.jpg&h=9d135403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n● 堀井雄二是有以《勇者鬥惡龍》的世界觀為主題、打造一個主題公園的，但要做起來的難度太高了。目前也有諸如《勇者鬥惡龍 VR》和環球影城的DQ主題項目，今後應該也會有新的體驗項目推出。"},{"pid":"de90ecf2073d9c4385eaf888cd804f6e5b5d3c71","tid":1249839,"uid":77769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:47:24.000Z","msg":"手機game都已經進入樽頸位時期<br />\n<br />\nse唔好搞咁多野啦<br />\n專心做返好家用機個邊先啦"},{"pid":"771fbee6af8431168e93a9efd8c63b6baf41d760","tid":1249839,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca738f4ea1bfeee986633cebb593d98dc26d310","tid":1249839,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T22:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1348d423059d2b462370821d4f3cd87ee23a000","tid":1249839,"uid":51753,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"de90ecf2073d9c4385eaf888cd804f6e5b5d3c71","tid":1249839,"uid":77769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:47:24.000Z","msg":"手機game都已經進入樽頸位時期<br />\n<br />\nse唔好搞咁多野啦<br />\n專心做返好家用機個邊先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T00:58:36.000Z","msg":"FGO 無樽頸"},{"pid":"1e28b8c98ec5fe5546c8792258b4860af8fdf1ca","tid":1249839,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79793cb8415420ca9880e34ac94b15c54bca3b8","tid":1249839,"uid":166947,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:38:41.000Z","msg":"老實講，你cut鳩曬所有ff以外嘅team放曬啲錢落去搵得仲多"},{"pid":"e7aa0c73fe354d87748878a06c7eeee26007082c","tid":1249839,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c79793cb8415420ca9880e34ac94b15c54bca3b8","tid":1249839,"uid":166947,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":